OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fthrough the evening, with plenty of
OL,7,Fclear skies overnight. Perhaps the odd
OL,8,Fshower returning during the early
OL,9,Fhours. A cooler night than of late
OL,10,Fwith lighter winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA fine day with bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudier by the
OL,14,Fevening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,15,FFeeling warmer as winds fall light for
OL,16,Fmany.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
