OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fcloudier day on Saturday, with light
OL,7,Fshowers. A mix of bright spells and a
OL,8,Ffew light showers for Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday. Temperatures generally above
OL,10,Faverage, so feeling rather warm.
